lead_paragraph: U.S. billionaire Wilbur Ross sold his entire shareholding in Bank of Ireland for almost half a billion euros on Tuesday, to almost triple the value of a shrewd investment made at the height of the euro zone crisis.

headline.main: U.S. Billionaire Wilbur Ross Cashes Out Bank of Ireland Stake
